precis:
Authority to enter into a CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENT with the province of
MANITOBA for the implementation of NATIONAL SAFETY CODE STANDARD NO. 14
(COMPLIANCE REVIEW - SAFETY RATING), a standard that ascribes a safety
performance rating to all truck and bus carriers.
